

After playing around with Node.JS, I decided to take a practical approach and build my knowledge on its software by changing my websites and commerce features with Node.JS & Express, and utilizing TDD/BDD Testing tools like Mocha, Chai, CasperJS and to explore/create the rest of node packages along the way that I might need to accomplish


Features to come:
- Rendering websites, pages and routes dynamically based on domain names
- API client to third party affiliate networks
- Shopzilla API Integration 
- Base Landing page backend
- Products / Affiliate Inventory backend
- Internal template management for site pages




